    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ocean Survivors is a pirate-themed, score-attack game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ocean is filled with greedy pirates who want to make a fortune. There's nowhere to run or hide, it's you against them. You must withstand the attacks of your enemies and survive. Gather gold to reach the top of the ranks while upgrading your ship in each run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your ship's arsenal</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/047f9c248745e55b4ec3d6150481e1e5.webp?t=1767882696\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/047f9c248745e55b4ec3d6150481e1e5.poster.webp?t=1767882696\" class=\"bb_img\" width=617 height=280 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combining your skills with acquired abilities, dominate the ocean</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/a704439c98fe46569aabf7a6eaa9a552.webp?t=1767882696\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/a704439c98fe46569aabf7a6eaa9a552.poster.webp?t=1767882696\" class=\"bb_img\" width=617 height=280 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gain the Edge by Utilizing Power-Ups</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/9c880def7253dc87c8023a26ec0ee785.webp?t=1767882696\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225320/extras/9c880def7253dc87c80